    Rearrange Selected by dragging&lt;br/&gt;
    Supports touch&lt;br/&gt;
    Data is list of sp_dependeny items
  &lt;/div&gt;

&lt;/div&gt;]]&gt;&lt;/template&gt;&lt;/sp_widget&gt;</payload>
